g/xaridor-chek-listi-b2b\"}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-8\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz\">Graver.uz</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 truncate max-w-xs\">B2B xaridor uchun korporativ sovg&#x27;alar chek-listi</li></ol></nav><header class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">B2B xaridor uchun korporativ sovg&#x27;alar chek-listi</h1><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500\"><time dateTime=\"2026-02-13\">12-fevral, 2026</time><span>1<!-- --> <!-- -->daqiqa o&#x27;qish</span><span>Graver.uz</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/blog/xaridor-chek-listi-b2b.jpg\" alt=\"B2B xaridor uchun korporativ sovg&#x27;alar chek-listi\" class=\"w-full aspect-video object-cover\" loading=\"eager\"/></div><article class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p>Ushbu maqola jamoaga jarayonni aniq boshqarishga yordam beradi: briefdan boshlab tiraj va topshirishgacha.</p>\n<p>Asosiy e&#x27;tibor amaliy yondashuvga qaratiladi: tanlov mezonlari, kelishuv bosqichlari va operatsion risklarni kamaytirish.</p>\n<h2>Boshlashdan oldin nimalar muhim</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Kampaniya maqsadi va natija metrikalari</li>\n<li>Qabul qiluvchilar segmenti va ustuvorliklar</li>\n<li>Byudjet va muddat cheklovlari</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Amaliy ish rejasi</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Brief va mahsulot tarkibini tasdiqlash</li>\n<li>Brendlash va test namunani kelishish</li>\n<li>Ishlab chiqarish va logistika jadvalini ishga tushirish</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Sifat va muddat nazorati</h2>\n<p>Topshirishdan oldin maketga moslik, qadoq sifati va personalizatsiya to&#x27;g&#x27;riligini namunaviy partiyada tekshiring.</p>\n<p><strong>Tanlash va ishga tushirishda yordam kerakmi?</strong> Kontaktlar bo&#x27;limi orqali murojaat qiling - jamoa tirajingizga mos ish rejasini tayyorlaydi.</p>\n<h2>Bog&#x27;liq maqolalar</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgani-qanday-tanlash\">Shuningdek qarang: bog&#x27;liq maqola</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/lazer-gravirovka-sovgalar\">Shuningdek qarang: bog&#x27;liq maqola</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/logotipli-sovga-toplami\">Shuningdek qarang: bog&#x27;liq maqola</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/welcome-pack-yangi-xodimlar\">Shuningdek qarang: bog&#x27;liq maqola</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/suvenir-brendlash\">Shuningdek qarang: bog&#x27;liq maqola</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/uz/blog/yangi-yil-sovga-goyalari\">Shuningdek qarang: bog&#x27;liq maqola</a></li>\n</ul></article><section class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">O&#x27;xshash maqolalar</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgani-qanday-tanlash\">Xodimlar uchun korporativ sovg&#x27;ani qanday tanlash</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Korporativ sovg&#x27;alarni tanlash bo&#x27;yicha amaliy tavsiyalar: logotipli mahsulotlar, byudjet, suvenir turlari.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/lazer-gravirovka-sovgalar\">Sovg&#x27;alarga lazer gravirovka: to&#x27;liq qo&#x27;llanma</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Korporativ sovg&#x27;alarga lazer gravirovka haqida hammasi: materiallar, texnologiyalar, maket tayyorlash, muddatlar.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/logotipli-sovga-toplami\">Kompaniya logotipli sovg&#x27;a to&#x27;plamlari</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Brendlangan korporativ sovg&#x27;a to&#x27;plamini qanday yig&#x27;ish: komplektatsiya, qadoqlash, turli byudjetlar uchun g&#x27;oyalar.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/welcome-pack-yangi-xodimlar\">Yangi xodimlar uchun Welcome Pack</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Welcome Pack tuzish bo&#x27;yicha qo&#x27;llanma: tarkibi, brendlash, tashkil etish. HR uchun amaliy maslahatlar.</p></article></div></section><div class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8\"><a class=\"text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition flex items-center\" href=\"/uz/blog\">← <!-- -->Blogga qaytish</a></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800 mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">Toshkentda biznes uchun premium lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik va brendlash</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Navigatsiya</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transiti